entries.femaleVariant: [Sit] What d'you recommend?
When Samurai started out, we spent every enny we had on guitars, strings, y'know...
G'morning.
The usual, Mr. Eurodyne?
Mhm. Double espresso, Jamaican blend. Nothin' else, no sugar.
You got it. And for you?
Same for me.
Just a regular coffee.
What he's havin'.
Just a regular coffee.
Great. Be right back with it.
[Stand]
Ehh, had almost nothin' left over for food, but we still went across the street every day, right to Caliente.
Johnny said we were so hungry and high we woulda eaten the cardboard boxes out from under the bums outside.
'Course he was wrong.
Nothing for now, thanks.
Nothin' for me, thanks.
No, no, no. She'll have what I'm having.
entries.maleVariant: No, no, no. He'll have what I'm having.

entries.femaleVariant: They really got to you, didn't they?
They're nice girls. What're you afraid of?
Dunno what this is about – my money's on money.
They don't back out now, let me know. I'll help.
This all stinks of a media set-up.
Not exaggerating, Ker? The girls just wanna have fun, sing your song to millions of adoring fans. You stand to gain here too.
entries.maleVariant: Not exaggerating, Ker? The girls just wanna have fun, sing your song. To millions of adoring fans. You stand to gain here too.

entries.femaleVariant: Don't believe for a millisec you torched that truck for art's sake. This is about money, isn't it? They screw you on the royalties?
entries.maleVariant: I don't believe for a millisec you torched that truck for art's sake. This is about money, isn't it? What, they screw ya on the royalties?

entries.femaleVariant: Tell you this much – if they don't back out now, gimme a call. We'll convince 'em another way.
entries.maleVariant: I'll tell you this much – if they don't back out now, gimme a call. We'll convince 'em another way.

entries.femaleVariant: Honestly, to me this all stinks of one big media play.
entries.maleVariant: Honestly? To me this all stinks of one big media play.

entries.femaleVariant: What if I'm a product just like those dolls? Drownin' in dirty money, 'stead of swimmin' in it.
No. You got a rocker's soul. I can feel it.
I'm with Johnny here.
Johnny's dead. Better think about what's important to you.
Look, not like we know each other that well, but trust me – you got a rocker's soul... and a rocker's balls.
Kerry, this shit's straight binary. Wanna be free? Keep the right to rebel?
Johnny's dead.
Better be goin'.
Look at this. Unlistenable. That trash is their biggest hit.
Fuck, anyone could churn out hits like that. Even you.
No, no, no, no, no. You know how Us Cracks got started? Bunch of MSM suits decided the world needed this dookie and so served it up sprinkled with millions of eddies.
World ate it up like it always does. And I gotta be part of that?
Somethin' tells me this isn't about Art-with-a-capital-A. Not about eds either. You're afraid, Kerry.
entries.maleVariant: Somethin' tells me this isn't about Art-with-a-capital-A. It's not about eds either. You're afraid, Kerry.

entries.femaleVariant: No clue what you're talkin' about. Got nothin' to do with money.
Thanks. Hope they're off my sonar now, 'cause if not... shit. Last thing I want is Johnny to've been right all along.
No! Not it at all!
Ah fuck... Sure hope you're wrong. 'Cause otherwise, Johnny woulda been right. From the get-go.
Oh, come on. Somehow you know where to find the gear truck of some Asian dolls doin' a cover of your song? Juicy little scandal for the media...
entries.maleVariant: Come on... Somehow you know where to find the gear truck of some Asian dolls doing a cover of your song? Juicy little scandal for the media...

entries.femaleVariant: Well... Johnny accused me of leaving Samurai for money. And fame.
And that's not something you'll admit to.
But that's not true.
No, no, it's true, won't lie. But he also said I'd be putting myself on a corp leash.
Heh, thanks...
This city doesn't forgive, it eats people alive. But you – well, you survived.
Never thought about it that way. You may be right, doll.
entries.maleVariant: Never thought about it that way. You may be right, man.

entries.femaleVariant: Shouldn'ta signed a multimillion-eddie deal with the biggest media conglomerate in the country.
entries.maleVariant: Then ya shouldn'ta signed a multimillion-eddie deal with the biggest media conglomerate in the country.

entries.femaleVariant: V, seriously think that? They got the rights to my songs, but fuck, not to me!
That's not how this city works. There's a contract. There's no "you."
You're wrong. And I'll prove it to ya.
Sure hope so, Ker.
So they say.
You're alive. Decide whose truth matters to you more – yours or someone else's.
entries.maleVariant: And you're alive. Decide whose truth matters more to you – yours or someone else's.

entries.femaleVariant: That a trick question?
Only if you don't have the 'nads to answer it honestly.
Thanks for, uh... you know.
Don't mention it.
So, what's good?
Hey, Rachel!
Stuffed our faces, downed joe by the gallon.
Sit, sit.
Make up your mind, woman.
[Drink]
So even after all the years you're still a regular. 'Bout time they hung your picture on the wall.
entries.maleVariant: So, even after all the years you're still a regular. S'about time they hung your picture on the wall.

entries.femaleVariant: Fuck... They really should.
Know this dump. Know that smell. But how...?
Whew! Shit... just comin' down now. Whew... fuckin' awesome.
Last time I felt like this was back in Memphis. Last tour, last concert, vibes from the crowd, me on stage...
Oh, fuck... Just thought about those Us Cracks cunts again. You think we got 'em?
They really getting to you that bad?
Well, if they don't back out now, let me know.
What's Johnny got to do with anything?
Johnny's dead. You're not.
Best case scenario, you know the game you're playin'. Worst – they're playin' you.
entries.maleVariant: Best case scenario, you know the game they're playin'. Worst – they're playin' you.

entries.femaleVariant: Ehh, if I'm afraid of anything, it's that Johnny might've been right.
I just can't stand the thought that... ugh, Johnny might've been right.
What's Johnny got to do with any of this?
The Us Cracks thing...
